import axios from "axios"; import React, { useState } from "react"; const Search = () => { const[id,setId] = useState() const getData = async(e) => { e.preventDefault() const resp = await axios.get(`https://63610b45af66cc87dc21409b.mockapi.io/property_data/${id}`) let data = resp.data console.log(data) } const arry = data return ( <>
{setId(e.target.value)}} placeholder="Enter ID to Search" />
{arry.map((value)=>{ return( <> ) })}
Sr. no Name of Property Adress of Property Property rent Property Details
{arry[value].id} {arry[value].name} {arry[value].address} {arry[value].rent} {arry[value].property_details}
) } export default Search;
